## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="4911e-111">下列範例會使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>建置的項目列出的<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem>含有國家 （地區） 名稱的項目，其中可能用來識別包含的任何詞彙。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4911e-111">The following example uses the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> element to build lists of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> elements containing country names, any one of which may be used to recognize the containing phrase.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4911e-112">然後此範例會將其中一個產生<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>歐洲國家 （地區） 和美國南部國家 （地區） 及其個別規則的物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4911e-112">The example then adds one of the resulting <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> objects to their respective rules for European countries and South American countries.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4911e-113">進一步上，此範例會使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>群組規則參考到的物件`ruleEurope`和`ruleSAmerica`成兩個替代項目清單，其中一個的其中可能用來辨識語音的輸入。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4911e-113">Further on, the example uses the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object to group rule references to `ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica` into a list of two alternatives, either one of which may be used to recognize spoken input.</span></span>  
  
```  
public void WorldSoccerWinners ()  
{  
  
  // Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
  // and set its scope to public.  
  SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
  SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
  winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
  // Add the introduction.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
  // Create the rule for the European nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"),   
    new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
  SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
  // Create the rule for the South American nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"),   
    new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
  SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
  // Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem   
    (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  
  
  // Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
  // the root rule of the document.  
  document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
  document.Root = winnerRule;  
}  
  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="4911e-116">下列範例會建立可辨識片語的文法 「 不具有贏了世界 Cup 民族 」 後面接著贏得世界 Cup 國家/地區的名稱。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4911e-116">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4911e-117">它會建立名為的公用規則`WorldCupWinner`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4911e-117">It creates a public rule named `WorldCupWinner`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4911e-118">接著會建立兩個<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule>物件，使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>物件，其中包含陣列的新<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem>物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4911e-118">It then creates two <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> objects using <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> objects that contain arrays of new <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4911e-119">若要查看此範例會產生的文法，請參閱<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4911e-119">To see the grammar that this example generates, see <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A>.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
 public void WorldSoccerWinners ()  
{  
  
  // Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
  // and set its scope to public.  
  SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
  SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
  winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
  // Add the introduction.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
  // Create the rule for the European nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"), new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
  SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
  // Create the rule for the South American nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"), new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
  SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
  // Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem   
    (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  
  
  // Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
  // the root rule of the document.  
  document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
  document.Root = winnerRule;  
}  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="4911e-124">下列範例會建立可辨識片語的文法 「 不具有贏了世界 Cup 民族 」 後面接著贏得世界 Cup 國家/地區的名稱。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4911e-124">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4911e-125">此範例會使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>要建立可接受的國家/地區中的名稱的陣列清單項目<xref:System.String>物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4911e-125">The example uses the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> element to build lists of acceptable country names from an array of <xref:System.String> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4911e-126">然後此範例會將其中一個產生<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>歐洲國家 （地區） 和美國南部國家 （地區） 及其個別規則的物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4911e-126">The example then adds one of the resulting <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> objects to their respective rules for European countries and South American countries.</span></span>  
  
```  
public void WorldSoccerWinners ()  
{  
    // Create a grammar from an SRGSDocument, create a new rule  
  // and set its scope to public.  
  SrgsDocument srgsGrammar = new SrgsDocument ();  
  SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule ("WorldCupWinner");  
  winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
  // Add the introduction.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add (new SrgsItem ("A nation that has won the world cup is"));  
  
  // Create the rule for the European nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf (new string[] {"England","France","Germany","Italy"});  
  SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
  // Create the rule for the South American nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf (new string[] {"Argentina","Brazil","Uruguay"});  
  SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
  // Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem   
    (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  
  
  // Add all the rules to the grammar and make winnerRule  
  // the root rule of the grammar.  
  srgsGrammar.Rules.Add (new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
  srgsGrammar.Root = winnerRule;  
}  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="4911e-131">下列範例會建立可辨識片語的文法 「 不具有贏了世界 Cup 民族 」 後面接著贏得世界 Cup 國家/地區的名稱。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4911e-131">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4911e-132">此範例會使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>物件來建立可接受的國家/地區中的名稱的陣列清單<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem>物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4911e-132">The example uses the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object to build lists of acceptable country names from an array of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4911e-133">使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf.Add%2A>方法，此範例會將附加<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem>至包含字串"義大利"<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>物件`oneOfEurope`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4911e-133">Using the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf.Add%2A> method, the example appends an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> that contains the string "Italy" to the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object `oneOfEurope`.</span></span>  
  
```  
public void WorldSoccerWinners ()  
{  
  
  // Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
  // and set its scope to public.  
  SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
  SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
  winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
  // Add the introduction.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
  // Create the rule for the European nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"),   
    new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany")});  
  oneOfEurope.Add(new SrgsItem("Italy"));  
  SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
  // Create the rule for the South American nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"),   
    new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
  SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
  // Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem   
    (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  
  
  // Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
  // the root rule of the document.  
  document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
  document.Root = winnerRule;  
}  
